{{Wireless embedded system |brand=Winstars |model=WS-WN577 |revision=A2 |series=AC750 |asin=B01MTXR9G6,B00W73PQGQ,B01EAHFTJK,B01G1BGS2K,B018HLRVBY |fcc_date=06/19/2015 |manuf_country=China |is_manuf=No |manuf=Intracom |manuf_model=525695 |type=access point, repeater, range extender |fcc_id=NZ3WS-WN566A2, 2ADQY525695 |pwr_v=100-240 |pwr_amp=0.1 |pwr_conn=AC (direct) |pwr_ac_hz=50/60 |cpu1_brand=Realtek |cpu1_model=RTL8881AN |fla1=4 |ram1=64 |wi1_chip1_brand=Realtek |wi1_chip1_model=RTL8881AN |wi1_802dot11_protocols=an+ac |wi1_txchains=1 |wi1_rxchains=1 |wi1_sstreams=1 |wi2_chip1_brand=Realtek |wi2_chip1_model=RTL8192ER |wi2_802dot11_protocols=bgn |wi2_txchains=2 |wi2_rxchains=2 |wi2_sstreams=2 |eth_cpu=true |sw_cpu=true |lan_speed=100M |lan_ports=1 |wan_speed=100M |wan_ports=1 |802dot11_protocols=abgn+ac |default_ip=192.168.10.1 |default_user=admin |default_pass=admin |oui=80:3F:5D }} {{TagLine|Wireless AC750 Dual-Band Range Extender}} :{{ProductPage|http://www.win-star.com/eshop/goods.php?id=190}} This model is re-branded under many names and is recognizable by its unique shape. *From FCC Cover letter doc: "The model WS-WN577A2 is only the plastic shell different from WS-WN566A2
(WS-WN566A2 with a Circular arc shell, WS-WN577A2 with a Square shell..." Rev A and Rev C have been noted but there is likely internal difference. {{see also|Maginon WLR-755 AC}}
